title: Portions of Sipsey Wilderness in Bankhead National Forest closed due to wildfire
text:
Published By: Al.com: Birmingham - Today 
Portions of the Sipsey Wilderness of the Bankhead National Forest are closed due to a wildfire, according to the U.S. Forest Service....
